    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Up for sale is a dependable vehicle in good overall condition, perfect for anyone seeking a reliable daily driver. The engine starts up without hesitation and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides consistent, solid shifts. The exterior shows some minor signs of regular use, but the paint still holds a nice luster, and the interior has been well-maintained with only light wear on the upholstery. All major electronics and safety features are fully functional. This is a well-cared-for car that is ready for many more miles on the road.",
