    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved by its single owner. The exterior paint is flawless, displaying a deep, mirror-like finish without a single scratch, chip, or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine, like-new condition, with the leather upholstery still firm and every electronic feature functioning perfectly. Mechanically, it is impeccable, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with all service records available, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from a brand-new car.",
