    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride in ownership, presenting in a state that balances performance with aesthetic appeal. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, with only a handful of minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. All glass is clear, and the alloy wheels are free of significant curbing. Inside, the interior remains a refined space; the premium upholstery is clean and firm, showing only light, natural softening on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system, has been tested and operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs with a smooth, consistent idle. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a full logbook available for review. The transmission provides seamless gear changes, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. With near-new tires and plenty of life left on the brake pads, this car is mechanically sound and ready for immediate enjoyment without the need for upcoming maintenance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
